## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
make install
{% if neo4j_type == 'docker' %}

# Start Neo4j (Docker)
make docker-up
{% elif neo4j_type == 'local' %}

# Start Neo4j (requires Node.js)
make neo4j-start
{% elif neo4j_type == 'aura' %}

# Neo4j Aura is already running in the cloud
# Credentials are in your .env file
{% endif %}

# Seed sample data
make seed

# Start the application
make start
```

- **Backend:** http://localhost:8000
- **Frontend:** http://localhost:3000
{% if neo4j_type == 'docker' or neo4j_type == 'local' %}
- **Neo4j Browser:** http://localhost:7474
{% elif neo4j_type == 'aura' %}
- **Neo4j Aura Console:** https://console.neo4j.io
{% endif %}

